Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}請全校學生務必在晚上八點前離校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}重複
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}請全校學生務必在晚上八點前離校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,主人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,難道魔之夜要在這片黑暗中降臨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,難道時間停止了的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好像不是的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這難道是主人對凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,凸守是主人的侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以抱有那樣的感情的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不過… 當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,越是禁忌就會讓人嚮往是世界的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我和勇太擁抱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你是冒牌主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.58,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,665)}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,繼冒牌森夏之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,連冒牌主人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是正牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,主人你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:04:00.92,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772,665)}Dark Flame Mastar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喜…喜歡上了… 漆黑烈焰使？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 凸守有個地方要去 先退下了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要攔我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,作為侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要對奪走了自己主人的心的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,施以黑暗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.62,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(788,665)}Dark Flame Mastar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,主人曾說過 因為有漆黑烈焰使在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,才能將邪王真眼保護至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:42.67,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(894,665)}Dark Flame Mastar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這份強烈的感情 一定也傳達給了漆黑烈焰使的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,侍奉了主人兩年多的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,侍從已經看穿了主人的一切哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王真眼是最強的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會進展順利的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說 你和小鳥遊同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,應該由我去告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是喜歡小鳥遊同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是因為她身材很好或者很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然她是個中二病 真心拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊 她不是個普通的中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她也有自己的煩惱 讓人覺得很可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 但這並不是出於同情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡一個人不需要理由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這話輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好噁心！ 好噁心！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊 人家好心好意陪你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,誰想找你商量了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是因為你說要是不坦白就在班上亂放流言！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你還真是幸運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,說到小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她的實力可是「小可愛」資格賽上的第四名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的事… 總有一天那樣的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾我沒有關於肉體接觸的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼呀什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,白癡嗎你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也要去了結一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,茴香學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那個… 請和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一起參加後夜祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,憑什麼我要看你演的肥皂劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是演戲！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你為什麼在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要為明天的演出做練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,富樫和小鳥遊同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,別提他們的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,凸守現在心情很不好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快來戰鬥的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,現在可沒有做那種事的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,比起那個 快把他們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他們倆回去了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.96,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(598,665)}Dark Flame Mastar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑烈焰使說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有很重要的話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}痛痛痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他這麼說的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,遵從吾之盟約 速速聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,遵從吾之盟約 速速聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,遵從吾之盟約 速速聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,魔導石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,能實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,從凸守那裡得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,願望的內容不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,誰都沒有問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,掉地上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,魔導石會因強大的願望而產生熱能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像帶了…傘吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有話要對勇太說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是跟最高機密有關的 重要的事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是… 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,事實上我也有話要說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 在這裡不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能就這麼沉默下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.47,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,665)}Schwarz Sechs Prototype Mark II
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,災厄之六 原型II！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這全名說的還真是流利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好這下面不是河川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,光… 在奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.55,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何も言わない背中に対して
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.55,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}望著你無言的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.93,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんて言えばいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.93,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不知該如何開口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:26.14,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好きになるのに　理由はないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:26.14,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明明愛上一個人沒有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.45,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気の無さに言い訳ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.45,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}卻因缺乏勇氣而滿口托詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.52,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流星群を眺めていたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.52,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遙望著漫天的流星群
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.65,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}キラキラって　音がするみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.65,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的閃光 彷彿伴隨著聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.57,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そういう気持ちの余韻すら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.57,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就連如此微不足道的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.62,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君となら分かち合える
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.62,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要與你一起 便能分享其中餘韻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.83,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}恋の欠片が　いま
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.83,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愛情的拼圖 此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.58,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一つに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.58,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:52.96,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}安っぽい言葉で飾っても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:52.96,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使用那廉價的言語來裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:59.34,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君に届かないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:59.34,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你或許也不會聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:05.31,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}でも何も言わないままだと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:05.31,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但如若保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.94,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君が消えちゃうかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.94,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你又彷彿會化為泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.98,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あの星みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.98,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如同那顆星星一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:17.23,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今どこで泣いてるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:17.23,ISCH,,0,0,0,,你現在在哪裡哭泣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:23.45,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}どうしたら　笑ってくれますか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:23.45,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要怎麼做 你才會解顏而笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:29.66,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}点を繋いで星座にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:29.66,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好想將那些點連成星座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:36.74,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}その指で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:36.74,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}用你的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:51.00,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背中合わせじゃなくて　こっちを向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:51.00,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請不要與我背對背 多希望你能轉向我這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:12:00.24,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)}そして隣を歩きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:12:00.24,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)}然後與我並肩同行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡 勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 應該是我先說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因邪王真眼的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,決定了這必須由我先開口的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.70,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,665)}Dark Flame Mastar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是漆黑烈焰使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王真眼是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 不算數不算數
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我好不容易想出來的 所以我要說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,被暗黑之炎所擁抱的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.10,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(538,665)}Dark Flame Mastar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,與漆黑烈焰使結下戀人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不玩了 總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,被暗黑之炎所擁抱的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:30.08,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,665)}Dark Flame Mastar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,與漆黑烈焰使結下戀人的契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這種情況不是應該到懷裡來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小拇指的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那就小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥你回來的真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 樟葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,原告有對被告抱有感情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,滿腦子都在想著儘早離開被告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,味道又變差了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,送你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在家裡說不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不能被六花聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是從義大利的本店寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,問我要不要去修行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有拒絕的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是厲害的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,之前一直在懷疑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,六花一定也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓她一個人住在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以媽媽會回來代替我跟她一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,六花的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得能順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,六花並不討厭她母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽好幾次想和六花談談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,關於隱瞞爸爸病情的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也向六花道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是怎麼了 十花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,由你來說的話 一定會有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,叫她變得正常點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,由你來說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,六花已經足夠正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看來 她那眼罩或許是為了保護自己的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對於這一切 六花她一定是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是總有一種無可奈何的朦朧感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才會那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,通過維持那個樣子 她在保護著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,保護什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但或許 是不想當作從未發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果聽從並認同了十花小姐和母親所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她不希望那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,結束有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,境界線和邪王真眼都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再怎麼尋找爸爸 也不可能見到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,認同她的說法 能解決得了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她所追求的東西 是永遠都得不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要認同這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也太不負責任了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 嚼勁十足的炒麵 熱氣騰騰的炒麵 要不要來一份？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,來 感謝您購買起司馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是大受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,別看她們那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,其實私底下女生之間的關係深如泥沼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才沒有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才是外脆裡稠的起司馬鈴薯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你油嘴滑舌地說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,話說小鳥遊同學和富樫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說是去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的演出會把你們那些顧客全部搶過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.02,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,665)}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這不是森夏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.44,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,665)}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,別叫我森夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,佐藤！？　還有鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊～ 初中畢業後就沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今年多少歲啦 716歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還在抓蜥蜴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,佐藤不也把嘴唇塗成紫色裝過病嬌少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 佐藤原來做過這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴木也說過「發現妖精啦～」之類的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,中二病之間的吵架可真是危險啊 都不知道會扯出什麼黑歷史來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的比試還沒有分出勝負的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天又給戰錘的威力增加了四倍的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好重的說！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,認同她的說法 能解決得了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要認同這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也太不負責任了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太 好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,別兩眼放光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,「死於黑暗之炎的懷抱吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太 發一個給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明明過會兒就得發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,死於黑暗之炎的懷抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這種東西會有什麼威力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 把兩腿張開半蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,扯住披風的布角用力搧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,死於黑暗之炎的懷抱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這次一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,任務差不多要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,到各自的工作崗位去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然沒什麼幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有一個叫小鳥遊六花的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正好去別的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 請將這個轉交給她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我這就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子應該還不想見到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是太不負責任了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這種地方發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正好來了很多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,眼罩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,取下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一年一度的才藝表演大會開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎亂入哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼事不宜遲 請第一號選手上臺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,第一號選手 一年3班 原田慎也 表演模仿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,模仿教務主任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啥啥啥 啥事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,表演 結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我和那個中二丫頭硬著頭皮混過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙可是真的使勁打過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}橫山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那麼這個四邊形ABCD啊 把這個AD和CD啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:12.34,註釋,,0,0,0,,{\pos(623,55)}de
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:12.34,註釋,,0,0,0,,{\pos(885,55)}de
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:12.34,註釋,,0,0,0,,{\pos(979,55)}de
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好 非常感謝 模仿得真像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}要是被老師聽到了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}裝傻～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}以上是來自原田慎也的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}有請二號選手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}NO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好的很遺憾～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}嘛 女人就跟天上星星一樣多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}NO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 沒聽見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}以上是來自一色誠的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}NO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然會說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這個便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一點溫溫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,感到沉甸甸的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像裝著滿滿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,關愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,第二號選手 一年級四班 一色誠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我要吶喊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,五月七日茴香學姊 請跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那 小鳥遊同學人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找找她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,富樫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}接下來是亂入的選手 有請三號選手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}一年四班 小鳥遊六花 表演唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:19.08,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}見上げてごらん夜の星を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:30.46,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}小さな星の 小さな光が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:42.23,ISJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ささやかな幸せをうたってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:19.08,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}抬頭看看吧 夜晚的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:30.46,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}小小星辰的那小小光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:42.23,ISCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}正歌頌著 那小小的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這是… 這是爸爸喜歡的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好 以上是一年4班小鳥遊六花的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這首歌曲中包含著什麼回憶嗎
